data.description: Seller now offering $2,500 credit towards closing costs! This spacious 3 bedroom 2.5 bath 2,284 sqft home features beautiful hardwood flooring, dramatic 17ft high ceilings, and an abundance of natural light throughout the house. The inviting eat-in kitchen is complete with stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, and a pantry. The open living space features high ceilings and plenty of windows to create ample room to relax at all times. An open staircase leads you upstairs to the second floor with an overlook to the living room below. The master suite featuring large double doors offers a walk in closet and luxury bath complete with double vanity, garden tub, and separate shower. Elsewhere on the second floor you will find two additional bedrooms, a bathroom, and covered balcony overlooking the neighborhood with plenty of space to relax during the afternoons. This home does need some TLC, but it is priced well below the comps in the neighborhood!
